  <section class="section-gap faq-section seo-faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head seo-modern-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">SEO FAQs</span>
        <h2>Common questions about our SEO services.</h2>
        <p>These answers cover timelines, pricing factors, local SEO, deliverables, and how Digi Web Tech approaches long-term organic growth.</p>
